msgctxt "seo_title"
msgid "Zeina Abi Assy - Director, Mozilla Festival | Mozilla Foundation"
msgstr "Zeina Abi Assy - Directrice du Mozilla Festival | Fondation Mozilla"

msgctxt "search_description"
msgid "Discover the global leaders behind Mozilla Foundation, working at the intersection of technology, ethics, and equity to shape a better digital future."
msgstr "Découvrez les leaders mondiaux de la Fondation Mozilla, qui œuvrent à l’intersection de la technologie, de l’éthique et de l’équité pour façonner un avenir numérique meilleur."

msgctxt "title"
msgid "Zeina Abi Assy"
msgstr "Zeina Abi Assy"

msgctxt "hero_title"
msgid "Zeina Abi Assy"
msgstr "Zeina Abi Assy"

msgctxt "hero_description"
msgid "Director, Mozilla Festival"
msgstr "Directrice du Mozilla Festival"

msgctxt "body.9ead4ce8-7292-412f-8702-f6c2f38093dc.left_column.97e38ee4-3d8c-4ea9-858b-185c183e8d31.image.alt_text"
msgid "Zeina Abi Assy's headshot"
msgstr "Photo portrait de Zeina Abi Assy"

msgctxt "body.9ead4ce8-7292-412f-8702-f6c2f38093dc.right_column.6a7f07fe-f474-46b5-bb76-75c4f023e03d"
msgid "Zeina Abi Assy is an award-winning curator, cultural producer, writer and designer."
msgstr "Zeina Abi Assy est une commissaire récompensée, une productrice culturelle, une autrice et une designer."

msgctxt "body.9ead4ce8-7292-412f-8702-f6c2f38093dc.right_column.6a7f07fe-f474-46b5-bb76-75c4f023e03d"
msgid ""
"She is the Director of the Mozilla Festival, a global gathering that convenes technologists, activists, policymakers, artists, entrepreneurs and researchers to imagine and build more ethical, mutual"
" futures for AI and the internet."
msgstr ""
"Elle est directrice du Mozilla Festival, un événement international qui rassemble technophiles, activistes, responsables politiques, artistes, entrepreneurs et chercheurs afin de concevoir et "
"façonner des futurs plus éthiques et solidaires pour l’IA et Internet."

msgctxt "body.9ead4ce8-7292-412f-8702-f6c2f38093dc.right_column.6a7f07fe-f474-46b5-bb76-75c4f023e03d"
msgid ""
"Previously, she was the Director of Interactive Programs at Tribeca Film Institute, where she co-curated Tribeca Film Festival’s Interactive Day and Immersive Exhibition, showcasing large-scale "
"installations and conversations at the intersection of emerging technology and storytelling. She has also consulted festivals and conferences across Europe and the SWANA region on themes related to "
"technology, storytelling and immersive media."
msgstr ""
"Elle a précédemment occupé le poste de directrice des programmes interactifs au Tribeca Film Institute, où elle a participé à la co-curation de la Journée Interactive et de l’Exposition Immersive du"
" Tribeca Film Festival, mettant en avant des installations de grande envergure ainsi que des discussions autour de la rencontre entre technologies émergentes et récit. Elle a par ailleurs conseillé "
"divers festivals et conférences en Europe et dans la région SWANA sur des sujets touchant à la technologie, à la narration et aux médias immersifs."

msgctxt "body.9ead4ce8-7292-412f-8702-f6c2f38093dc.right_column.6a7f07fe-f474-46b5-bb76-75c4f023e03d"
msgid "Her writing has appeared in the printed anthologies <i>Arab Women Voice New Realities</i> and <i>We Call to the Eye &amp; the Night</i>."
msgstr "Ses textes figurent dans les recueils imprimés <i>Arab Women Voice New Realities</i> et <i>We Call to the Eye & the Night</i>."
